1
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:28,000
[Episode 8: I've Liked You for a Long Time...
The Romantic Kind.]

2
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,079
Yu Lei.

3
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:30,920
You're drunk.

4
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:33,159
Let's talk tomorrow.

5
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:34,239
No, today.

6
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:36,039
Right now.

7
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,000
You...

8
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,079
I-I'm sorry.

9
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:56,040
I... You...

10
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:58,480
- I...
- Sorry for what?

11
00:01:59,832 --> 00:02:02,386
Because we're both... drunk.

12
00:02:02,386 --> 00:02:04,599
Why don't we wait until we've sobered up?

13
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:06,399
And then...

14
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:10,000
You kissed me.

15
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,159
I kissed you back.

16
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,599
We're even.

17
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:14,399
No need to be sorry.

18
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,719
He Jin.

19
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:20,719
What are you doing here?

20
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:23,000
Since I'm already here,

21
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,239
aren't you going to invite me in?

22
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,415
He Jin.

23
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:33,891
Why have you been drinking so much?

24
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,560
It's late at night. You should be asleep.

25
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,599
Why are you here making a drunken scene?

26
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:42,559
I thought... I'd only find Chen Ke.

27
00:03:42,559 --> 00:03:44,599
I didn't expect you to be here too.

28
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:45,960
This is great.

29
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,440
Saves me the trouble.

30
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:50,180
He Jin. What are you doing?

31
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:53,182
You two made my life a living hell.

32
00:03:53,182 --> 00:03:55,590
So I'm going to make your lives
a living hell too.

33
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:46,039
Ke Ke! Ke Ke!

34
00:04:46,039 --> 00:04:47,719
Ke Ke! What do we do?

35
00:04:47,719 --> 00:04:50,479
Doctor! Quick! Stop the bleeding!

36
00:04:50,479 --> 00:04:52,440
Ke Ke... Ke Ke...

37
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:54,000
Wake up.

38
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,440
Talk to me.

39
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:57,919
The bleeding won't stop.

40
00:04:57,919 --> 00:04:58,960
Ke Ke.

41
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,760
Ke Ke.

42
00:05:36,919 --> 00:05:39,680
The reason I've become like this
is all their fault!

43
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,200
Calm down.

44
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,619
First, answer our questions.

45
00:05:42,619 --> 00:05:44,719
Why did you hurt your classmate?

46
00:05:44,719 --> 00:05:47,560
They made everyone exclude me.

47
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:51,039
I just taught Chen Ke a small lesson.

48
00:05:51,039 --> 00:05:54,120
And he and Yu Lei went to the school
and reported me together.

49
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,680
They got me disciplined.

50
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,200
Just because of that?

51
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,880
You go to such a good school.

52
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,280
Why don't you know how to cherish it?

53
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:03,436
They were deliberately
making my life difficult!

54
00:06:03,436 --> 00:06:07,039
I wanted to get along with them peacefully.

55
00:06:07,039 --> 00:06:09,640
But from the very first day of school,

56
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,839
Chen Ke looked down on me.

57
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:16,320
And that Yu Lei bullied me with Chen Ke.

58
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:18,239
- They laughed at me!
- Young man.

59
00:06:18,239 --> 00:06:20,039
Calm down.

60
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:23,719
I got disciplined.

61
00:06:23,719 --> 00:06:25,960
And they told my family.

62
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:28,200
I can't face my family anymore.

63
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:30,520
And I can't stay at school either.

64
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:33,039
What's the difference
between living and being dead?

65
00:06:33,039 --> 00:06:34,919
Since they want to ruin my life,

66
00:06:34,919 --> 00:06:37,719
I won't let them live in peace either!

67
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:43,988
[Operation in Progress]

68
00:06:54,731 --> 00:06:56,331
[Quiet]

69
00:07:00,799 --> 00:07:02,359
Lei Lei.

70
00:07:02,359 --> 00:07:04,000
What happened?

71
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,412
How did Chen Ke suddenly
get stabbed by He Jin?

72
00:07:08,052 --> 00:07:10,080
Are you hurt anywhere?

73
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,584
Sis.

74
00:07:12,599 --> 00:07:14,560
I'm fine.

75
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:17,120
They're still trying to save Chen Ke.

76
00:07:25,599 --> 00:07:27,279
It's okay.

77
00:07:27,279 --> 00:07:28,799
It's okay.

78
00:07:28,799 --> 00:07:31,039
Chen Ke will be okay.

79
00:07:31,039 --> 00:07:33,199
You'll both be okay.

80
00:07:40,599 --> 00:07:42,799
I can't believe that scumbag He Jin
is so twisted.

81
00:07:42,799 --> 00:07:44,919
He's lucky that he got caught.

82
00:07:44,919 --> 00:07:48,039
If I had gotten my hands on him,
I would've knocked his lights out.

83
00:07:48,039 --> 00:07:49,279
Enough already.

84
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,799
Look at the time.

85
00:07:50,799 --> 00:07:53,159
Let Yu Lei get some rest.

86
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,320
Lei Lei.

87
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,080
Chen Ke's a good guy. He'll be fine.

88
00:07:58,080 --> 00:08:00,120
He'll definitely be okay.

89
00:08:03,359 --> 00:08:05,360
Is the patient's family here?

90
00:08:06,919 --> 00:08:09,120
Doctor. How is he?

91
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,640
Who is the patient's family?

92
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,680
Doctor. We're all Chen Ke's classmates.

93
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,919
His family doesn't live here.
They can't get here right away.

94
00:08:14,919 --> 00:08:16,599
If there's any news, you can tell us first.

95
00:08:16,599 --> 00:08:18,839
Right. I... I'm his brother.

96
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:20,760
His real brother.

97
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:23,120
Doctor. How is he really doing?

98
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,279
Here's the situation.

99
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:26,399
We're still doing everything
we can to save him.

100
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:28,479
However, the patient has lost a lot of blood.

101
00:08:28,479 --> 00:08:30,120
He needs a transfusion during the surgery.

102
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,479
You should prepare yourselves.

103
00:08:31,479 --> 00:08:32,719
And please notify his family
as soon as possible.

104
00:08:32,719 --> 00:08:34,759
Do you need to draw blood? Take mine.

105
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:36,759
I'm type B too. I'm the same as him.

106
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:38,160
Doctor, I'm strong. I'm also type B.

107
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,680
I'm type O. That should work too, right?

108
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:42,050
Alright, everyone, please calm down.

109
00:08:42,050 --> 00:08:43,799
We have a blood bank here.

110
00:09:25,878 --> 00:09:27,717
Grandma.

111
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:37,759
Grandma, I miss you so much.

112
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:40,056
Grandma misses you too.

113
00:09:40,056 --> 00:09:41,280
Grandma.

114
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:45,359
The song you taught me,
I can play it really well now.

115
00:09:45,359 --> 00:09:46,519
That's wonderful.

116
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:49,000
Grandma is so proud of you.

117
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,132
Hemostat.

118
00:10:08,719 --> 00:10:09,759
Doctor.

119
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:12,479
How is Chen Ke doing?

120
00:10:12,479 --> 00:10:14,960
Doctor. How is he? He's okay, right?

121
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,920
The surgery was successful.

122
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,839
But because he lost so much blood,
he needs to rest quietly.

123
00:10:17,839 --> 00:10:19,679
Please don't disturb him.

124
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:31,879
Lei Lei.

125
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:32,960
- Lei Lei.
- Yu Lei.

126
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,435
Yu Lei.

127
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,560
Chen Ke.

128
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,839
Chen Ke.

129
00:10:39,839 --> 00:10:41,479
Chen Ke.

130
00:10:41,479 --> 00:10:45,400
Look. The children outside
are calling for you.

131
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:48,879
No. Right now, I just want to be with you.

132
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:52,119
I haven't seen you in so long.

133
00:10:52,119 --> 00:10:53,999
Grandma.

134
00:10:53,999 --> 00:10:56,680
Grandma wants to be with you too.

135
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,479
But not right now.

136
00:10:58,479 --> 00:11:01,560
Grandma.
Don't you want me to stay with you?

137
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:05,080
My child. You still have a long time.

138
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,599
But it shouldn't be spent here.

139
00:11:07,599 --> 00:11:09,200
Go back.

140
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,920
Go over there.

141
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:13,280
There are people who love you and need you.

142
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:16,719
Don't worry. Grandma will always be here.

143
00:11:16,719 --> 00:11:19,800
When the time really comes
for us to be together,

144
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:22,440
we'll see each other again.

145
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,119
Okay?

146
00:11:24,119 --> 00:11:26,359
Go on. The children are calling you.

147
00:11:26,359 --> 00:11:27,838
Go.

148
00:11:40,925 --> 00:11:42,549
Hey.

149
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:52,040
It was like I was in a very long dream.

150
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:54,680
Even after opening my eyes,

151
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:58,320
I couldn't be sure if the dream
was really over.

152
00:11:58,320 --> 00:12:03,119
It wasn't until I saw Yu Lei,
that I knew for sure.

153
00:12:03,119 --> 00:12:05,680
He's my anchor to reality.

154
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,280
And my reason for living.

155
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,599
Ke Ke.

156
00:12:08,599 --> 00:12:10,280
You're awake.

157
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,519
I-I'll go get someone.

158
00:12:11,519 --> 00:12:13,839
Yu Lei. Yu Lei.

159
00:12:13,839 --> 00:12:15,639
Wait.

160
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:17,760
Let me get a good look at you.

161
00:12:23,239 --> 00:12:24,879
Ke Ke.

162
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,920
I'm sorry.

163
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:29,839
I didn't protect you.

164
00:12:29,839 --> 00:12:31,320
It's okay.

165
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,800
I'm fine.

166
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:35,040
Don't blame yourself.

167
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:39,120
If you keep being like this,
I won't talk to you anymore.

168
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,932
How long have you been with me?

169
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,639
All night.

170
00:12:50,639 --> 00:12:53,440
Actually, everyone came to see you.

171
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:55,955
But I sent them all away.

172
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,719
The first person you saw
when you opened your eyes

173
00:12:58,719 --> 00:13:00,559
has to be me.

174
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,599
You have no idea.

175
00:13:02,599 --> 00:13:04,879
Last night, in the middle of your surgery,

176
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:07,119
the doctor said
you needed a blood transfusion.

177
00:13:07,119 --> 00:13:08,680
It scared everyone to death.

178
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,480
So you're saying...

179
00:13:11,119 --> 00:13:13,319
you gave me blood?

180
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,639
Of course I wanted to.

181
00:13:15,639 --> 00:13:16,999
As long as it could save you,

182
00:13:16,999 --> 00:13:19,239
I would've given you
all the blood in my body.

183
00:13:19,239 --> 00:13:20,654
Anything.

184
00:13:21,479 --> 00:13:24,960
But... the doctor said...

185
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,639
they could just get more from the blood bank.

186
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:32,039
He also said we college kids
watch too much TV.

187
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:43,839
Chen Ke's mom came all the way
from their hometown to take care of him.

188
00:13:43,839 --> 00:13:46,040
So why is Yu Lei still
hanging around the hospital?

189
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:48,760
What? Jealous?

190
00:13:49,479 --> 00:13:51,047
None of your business.

191
00:14:04,599 --> 00:14:06,560
Does it still hurt, Ke Ke?

192
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:09,359
Bro. I'm fine, really.

193
00:14:09,359 --> 00:14:11,400
You've been at the hospital this whole time.

194
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:13,560
You should go home and get some rest.

195
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:16,319
It's okay. I can handle it.

196
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,999
Xiao Lei, look at you.

197
00:14:18,999 --> 00:14:21,200
You've been watching over Ke Ke for days.

198
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:23,080
You've gotten so thin.

199
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,759
Now that I'm here, you should hurry home.

200
00:14:25,759 --> 00:14:27,719
Even just to get a good night's sleep.

201
00:14:27,719 --> 00:14:29,599
- Yeah.
- Exactly.

202
00:14:29,599 --> 00:14:31,239
Auntie is right.

203
00:14:31,239 --> 00:14:32,560
What are you guys doing here?

204
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,879
What do you think?

205
00:14:33,879 --> 00:14:35,639
Here.

206
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:37,400
And you two are...

207
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:41,400
Auntie, we're Chen Ke's... friends.

208
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,080
Good friends. Best buds.

209
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,719
Thank you for coming to see Ke Ke.

210
00:14:44,719 --> 00:14:46,920
I'll go get you some fruit.

211
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,119
Auntie, don't worry about it.

212
00:14:48,119 --> 00:14:49,400
We can help ourselves.

213
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,920
Please, don't go to any trouble.

214
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:54,479
Ke Ke, I didn't know
you had so many good friends.

215
00:14:54,479 --> 00:14:56,359
Of course, Auntie. Don't you worry.

216
00:14:56,359 --> 00:14:59,080
At school, Ke Ke is really popular.

217
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,560
You can relax too.

218
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:01,639
Han Han and I are here
to take over for you.

219
00:15:01,639 --> 00:15:03,639
- That's right.
- You haven't slept properly in days.

220
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:05,879
- Go home and rest.
- But I...

221
00:15:05,879 --> 00:15:07,993
Bro. Go home and get some rest.

222
00:15:07,993 --> 00:15:10,800
And bring me a change of clothes
while you're at it.

223
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:11,960
All right, then.

224
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,359
Auntie, I'll be back later.

225
00:15:13,359 --> 00:15:14,800
Okay. Get some sleep.

226
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,639
- Okay.
- Go on, go on.

227
00:15:16,639 --> 00:15:17,960
Don't worry. Go on home.

228
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,840
Get some sleep.

229
00:15:36,624 --> 00:15:37,920
Look at this.

230
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,720
This is hilarious.

231
00:15:40,479 --> 00:15:41,999
Chen Ke,

232
00:15:41,999 --> 00:15:44,719
you looked so different
when you were little...

233
00:15:44,719 --> 00:15:45,879
compared to now.

234
00:15:45,879 --> 00:15:47,080
Isn't that the truth?

235
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:49,400
He was such a chubby-cheeked kid.

236
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:50,999
Nothing like how he is now.

237
00:15:50,999 --> 00:15:54,200
Mom, why do you always show people this?

238
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:57,920
I've been looking for this photo
for a long time and finally found it.

239
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,160
Look at this one.

240
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:01,960
This is Chen Ke and Yu Lei
when they were little.

241
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:02,960
This one right here.

242
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:05,519
No way.

243
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:09,080
Chen Ke, you knew Yu Lei when you were kids?

244
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:12,147
It was only last time when Ke Ke came home,

245
00:16:12,147 --> 00:16:15,280
that we even remembered it.

246
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:17,080
It's fate, isn't it?

247
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,880
Right?

248
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:22,879
Destined to be together,
even from a thousand miles away.

249
00:16:22,879 --> 00:16:25,760
Chen Ke, I really envy you guys.

250
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:07,597
[Chopin]

251
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:14,747
[Student Exchange Program]

252
00:17:22,999 --> 00:17:27,440
Even now, I still wake up from nightmares,

253
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:31,279
worried that on that night,
I had lost Chen Ke forever.

254
00:17:31,279 --> 00:17:34,360
It's not until I see his face
in the hospital room every day,

255
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:37,559
when he smiles at me, and talks to me,

256
00:17:37,559 --> 00:17:41,039
that I can be sure he's still here.

257
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:43,799
I don't know what the future holds.

258
00:17:43,799 --> 00:17:46,920
The only thing I'm sure of
is that I want to hold on to him tightly,

259
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,776
and never let go.

260
00:17:51,519 --> 00:17:53,120
We've been so busy talking,
we're out of water.

261
00:17:53,120 --> 00:17:55,079
I'll go get some more.

262
00:17:56,559 --> 00:17:58,479
Auntie, I'll go with you.

263
00:17:58,479 --> 00:18:00,910
All right. Let's go together.

264
00:18:11,479 --> 00:18:14,719
So, you have something to say to me?

265
00:18:14,719 --> 00:18:16,568
You could tell?

266
00:18:17,479 --> 00:18:19,279
I guess so.

267
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:24,719
Chen Ke, do you know how Yu Lei and I
first met?

268
00:18:24,719 --> 00:18:27,960
We met in a local chat room.

269
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,719
We found out we both
got into Mingde University.

270
00:18:29,719 --> 00:18:32,319
Then, we added each other on QQ.

271
00:18:33,999 --> 00:18:35,819
From online to real life,

272
00:18:35,819 --> 00:18:39,079
I never thought
I could like someone so much.

273
00:18:39,079 --> 00:18:40,503
No wonder.

274
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:46,121
Clearly, I was the one who knew him first.

275
00:18:48,479 --> 00:18:51,559
And he really disliked you at the beginning.

276
00:18:51,559 --> 00:18:53,400
But somehow, later on,
you two got closer and closer,

277
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,360
and became more intimate.

278
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:56,759
I couldn't accept it.

279
00:18:56,759 --> 00:18:59,880
I wanted to compete with you over everything.

280
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:03,200
Ouyang Han, you're a great person.

281
00:19:04,479 --> 00:19:05,960
Of course I know that.

282
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,479
I know I'm excellent.

283
00:19:07,479 --> 00:19:10,599
It's just that Yu Lei is biased.

284
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,200
Did you know?

285
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:15,880
On Yu Lei's birthday, after you guys left,

286
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:18,400
I even confessed my feelings to him.

287
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:21,559
But he just doesn't see me that way at all.

288
00:19:21,559 --> 00:19:23,085
Really?

289
00:19:24,719 --> 00:19:28,239
At the time, I felt so defeated.

290
00:19:28,239 --> 00:19:31,279
I couldn't figure out where I went wrong.

291
00:19:31,279 --> 00:19:33,121
But now I realize,

292
00:19:33,121 --> 00:19:35,519
with things like this,
it's not about winning or losing.

293
00:19:35,519 --> 00:19:37,760
It's about who you like.

294
00:19:39,479 --> 00:19:43,479
After seeing what happened to you
and how worried Yu Lei was,

295
00:19:43,479 --> 00:19:47,719
and then seeing that you two
have known each other since you were kids,

296
00:19:47,719 --> 00:19:51,799
I realized the bond between you and Yu Lei

297
00:19:51,799 --> 00:19:54,319
is something no one can ever come close to.

298
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:57,440
Is that what a bond is?

299
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,920
A bond.

300
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,880
An entanglement.

301
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:02,719
Fate.

302
00:20:02,719 --> 00:20:04,759
Call your relationship whatever you want.

303
00:20:04,759 --> 00:20:07,680
Anyway, that's just how it is.

304
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:10,160
No one else can get in between you.

305
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:12,319
Even if they tried, they couldn't.

306
00:20:12,319 --> 00:20:15,719
Anyway, I've finally figured it out.

307
00:20:15,719 --> 00:20:17,920
I don't have time to
compete with you anymore.

308
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:20,200
I don't want to be the next Chen Ke.

309
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:22,534
I want to be the one and only Ouyang Han.

310
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:27,518
So, will you...

311
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:32,640
Will you be my friend?

312
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:37,319
We already are.

313
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:45,138
So, actually, are you...

314
00:20:45,138 --> 00:20:48,230
Are you and Yu Lei already together?

315
00:21:32,239 --> 00:21:37,680
[A diary entry with VERY messy handwriting
about the first day of classes]

316
00:21:43,759 --> 00:21:48,039
Today, that boy named Yu Lei
came to the practice room,

317
00:21:48,039 --> 00:21:50,359
and asked me what piece I was playing.

318
00:21:51,759 --> 00:21:53,799
It's kind of funny.

319
00:21:53,799 --> 00:21:56,920
Even though we'd run into each other
a few times,

320
00:21:56,920 --> 00:22:01,440
this was the first time
we'd ever had a real conversation.

321
00:22:02,079 --> 00:22:05,200
It turns out he likes that piece too.

322
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:09,079
I suddenly felt like
I'd met a kindred spirit.

323
00:22:09,079 --> 00:22:11,200
I was so happy.

324
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:20,200
Today, Yu Lei took me on a trip.

325
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:23,719
I don't know why, but around him,

326
00:22:23,719 --> 00:22:26,759
I feel like a clumsy penguin.

327
00:22:26,759 --> 00:22:32,879
At night, we all had drinks, ate hot pot,
and watched a movie.

328
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:38,200
I never knew hanging out with everyone
could be so much fun.

329
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:42,960
All of this was thanks to Yu Lei.

330
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:48,479
To me, he seems like someone special.

331
00:22:48,479 --> 00:22:52,839
It's a feeling I've never had before.

332
00:23:01,039 --> 00:23:06,519
Seeing Yu Lei being close with someone else
made me feel so upset.

333
00:23:06,519 --> 00:23:08,640
What's wrong with me?

334
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:23,039
Today, Yu Lei told me
that he could be like a real brother to me.

335
00:23:23,039 --> 00:23:28,000
Is this really the limit of our relationship?

336
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:38,880
From strangers, to friends,
and then to family.

337
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:41,636
We've become so close,

338
00:23:41,636 --> 00:23:46,119
so why do I still feel
this deep sense of longing?

339
00:23:48,360 --> 00:23:49,999
Ke Ke.

340
00:23:49,999 --> 00:23:52,400
So this is how you felt.

341
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:10,479
Why are you here alone?

342
00:24:10,479 --> 00:24:11,799
Where's your mom?

343
00:24:11,799 --> 00:24:12,960
My mom went to get something to eat.

344
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:15,440
She said she'd pick up a few things too.

345
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:17,359
She'll probably take a while.

346
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,920
Ke Ke.

347
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:26,079
I'm so sorry.

348
00:24:26,079 --> 00:24:28,079
What are you...

349
00:24:30,279 --> 00:24:31,640
I'm sorry.

350
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:35,119
I never knew that you kept a diary.

351
00:24:35,759 --> 00:24:39,840
I swear, I absolutely didn't mean to
invade your privacy.

352
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:45,079
I... I just... I just couldn't help myself.

353
00:24:45,079 --> 00:24:47,600
So, please forgive me.

354
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:49,400
You know everything now?

355
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,719
Yeah.

356
00:24:51,719 --> 00:24:53,840
I'm sorry.

357
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,479
I have so many regrets.

358
00:24:55,479 --> 00:24:57,559
Regret what?

359
00:24:59,799 --> 00:25:04,719
I... I regret not telling you sooner
about how I felt.

360
00:25:04,719 --> 00:25:08,279
My feelings for you...
They're not just brotherly or friendly.

361
00:25:08,279 --> 00:25:10,600
I don't want to see you get hurt,

362
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,759
and I don't want you to be lonely.

363
00:25:12,759 --> 00:25:14,759
I want to make you laugh every day.

364
00:25:14,759 --> 00:25:17,319
I want to take you to see the world.

365
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,360
Ke Ke.

366
00:25:19,360 --> 00:25:23,559
I realized I've been in love with you
for a long time.

367
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:26,039
The romantic kind of love.

368
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,799
What did you and Chen Ke talk about?

369
00:26:23,799 --> 00:26:25,799
What was so secretive
that I couldn't hear it?

370
00:26:25,799 --> 00:26:28,759
Oh. That's our secret.

371
00:26:28,759 --> 00:26:30,440
What's it to you?

372
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:32,871
Why do you have so many secrets?

373
00:26:34,840 --> 00:26:37,996
Make a guess then.
What could Chen Ke and I possibly talk about?

374
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:45,200
You talked about Yu Lei, didn't you?

375
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,279
Tell me.

376
00:26:46,279 --> 00:26:48,640
Do you still have feelings for Yu Lei?

377
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,759
You used visiting Chen Ke as an excuse

378
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:52,640
to go see Yu Lei, didn't you?

379
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:55,160
But Yu Lei had left,
so you were disappointed.

380
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,999
So you took it out on Chen Ke?

381
00:26:56,999 --> 00:26:59,480
Are you crazy?

382
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,360
I know.

383
00:27:02,360 --> 00:27:03,799
You're jealous, aren't you?

384
00:27:03,799 --> 00:27:05,327
I...

385
00:27:08,360 --> 00:27:09,440
What are you doing?

386
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:11,840
I'll show you what I look like
when I'm jealous.

387
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:13,799
In broad daylight, what are you, crazy?

388
00:27:13,799 --> 00:27:16,023
Seeing you makes me crazy.
Is that a problem?

389
00:27:32,039 --> 00:27:33,360
What?

390
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,671
You like it.

391
00:27:35,719 --> 00:27:38,400
Yu Lei. Do you still remember?

392
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:42,200
This was our first real conversation.

393
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,479
I recorded it by accident.

394
00:27:44,479 --> 00:27:48,960
But I could never bring myself
to record over it.

395
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:51,079
I was always confused

396
00:27:51,079 --> 00:27:53,799
about what my feelings for you really were.

397
00:27:53,799 --> 00:27:55,600
My senior encouraged me.

398
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:57,440
Instead of struggling with it alone,

399
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,160
she told me to be brave and express myself.

400
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:03,079
For example,
by making a special gift for you.

401
00:28:03,079 --> 00:28:05,360
But I'm not as bold as she is.

402
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:09,360
I've been preparing the gift for a long time.

403
00:28:09,360 --> 00:28:10,400
A gift?

404
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,440
What is it?

405
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:15,120
It's... It's not completely ready yet.

406
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:17,920
And I don't know if you'll like it.

407
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,039
It's okay.

408
00:28:19,039 --> 00:28:21,680
As long as it's from you, I'll like anything.

409
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:24,799
No. Not yet.

410
00:28:24,799 --> 00:28:25,960
Let me hear it.

411
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:29,080
♫ Moving through endless corners ♫

412
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:33,160
♫ You are the light from the sun ♫

413
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:36,880
♫ Shining on the entire river of stars ♫

414
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:40,600
♫ Your eyes are like the universe ♫

415
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:44,480
♫ That make me fall with just one glance ♫

416
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:48,200
♫ What should I do? ♫

417
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:51,479
Sorry. I haven't figured out the ending yet.

418
00:28:51,479 --> 00:28:53,359
It's beautiful.

419
00:28:55,319 --> 00:28:56,680
What piece is this?

420
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:59,440
I've never heard it before.

421
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:01,120
Is it Bach?

422
00:29:01,120 --> 00:29:02,719
Beethoven?

423
00:29:02,719 --> 00:29:04,759
Or Mozart?

424
00:29:04,759 --> 00:29:06,120
None of them.

425
00:29:06,120 --> 00:29:08,960
I just hummed it one day during the break.

426
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:13,079
I thought the melody was nice,
so I wrote it down.

427
00:29:13,079 --> 00:29:15,060
I was thinking that
when I come back from the break,

428
00:29:15,060 --> 00:29:17,120
I'd play it for you first.

429
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:21,039
So this is the gift you prepared?
It's so beautiful.

430
00:29:21,039 --> 00:29:23,799
I've been trying to record
a perfect version for you,

431
00:29:23,799 --> 00:29:25,960
but I haven't been able to get it right.

432
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:28,719
On this cassette tape,
it's at best just a demo.

433
00:29:28,719 --> 00:29:30,279
It's okay.

434
00:29:30,279 --> 00:29:33,119
As long as it's you, it's the best version.

435
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:41,400
But the lyrics seem a little sad.

436
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:43,319
Since we're so in love,

437
00:29:43,319 --> 00:29:45,799
shouldn't we make them a bit sweeter?

438
00:29:45,799 --> 00:29:49,279
But love isn't just about the sweet moments.

439
00:29:49,279 --> 00:29:51,680
There's also sadness, and sorrow.

440
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:54,120
It awakens something deep inside you,

441
00:29:54,120 --> 00:29:56,680
like possessiveness,
and the desire for control.

442
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:59,239
It's because of these imperfect things

443
00:29:59,239 --> 00:30:02,079
that we learn to cherish
the beautiful moments we have now.

444
00:30:02,079 --> 00:30:03,879
Don't you think?

445
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,239
Ke Ke.

446
00:30:08,239 --> 00:30:11,239
You are both a gift from the heavens,

447
00:30:11,239 --> 00:30:13,680
and a trial sent by fate.

448
00:30:14,519 --> 00:30:17,360
I can't bear to lose you, or let you go.

449
00:30:17,360 --> 00:30:19,920
It seems our love was written in the stars.

450
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:22,160
This feeling is inescapable.

451
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:24,680
- It leaves my mind for but a moment...
- Stop.

452
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:27,519
Why are you reciting poetry all of a sudden?
It's so cheesy.

453
00:30:27,519 --> 00:30:28,880
Hey, you were the one
being all poetic earlier.

454
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,879
Wasn't that just as cheesy?

455
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:35,680
Alright, alright. No more cheesy lines.

456
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:38,680
Let's get right to it. Okay?

457
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,440
Sis.

458
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:53,479
When you get there, you have to promise
to take good care of yourself.

459
00:30:53,479 --> 00:30:55,160
Remember to call me.

460
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,600
Wait, no, the time difference.

461
00:30:56,600 --> 00:30:59,079
- Then write me letters.
- Okay.

462
00:30:59,079 --> 00:31:01,519
And I heard the winters there are freezing.

463
00:31:01,519 --> 00:31:03,440
You have to remember to bundle up.

464
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:05,600
And wear the scarf I gave you, okay?

465
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:07,120
It's really warm.

466
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:08,680
- Also...
- Alright.

467
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:10,799
Yu Lei, you've been talking to her forever.

468
00:31:10,799 --> 00:31:13,039
Give the rest of us some time
to say our goodbyes.

469
00:31:13,039 --> 00:31:14,440
Seriously.

470
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,479
Shut up.

471
00:31:15,479 --> 00:31:18,359
What's wrong with me
saying a few more words to her?

472
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:20,519
Wait a second.

473
00:31:20,519 --> 00:31:22,600
What are you even doing here?

474
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:23,700
Are you two even that close?

475
00:31:23,700 --> 00:31:25,920
I... Of course we're close.

476
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:28,079
We've hung out before.

477
00:31:28,079 --> 00:31:31,440
And... we built the school stage together.
Right?

478
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:35,759
So, Senior,
I've never had the courage to say this,

479
00:31:35,759 --> 00:31:39,920
but the first time I met you,
I thought you were so awesome.

480
00:31:40,559 --> 00:31:43,319
So, well... have a safe trip.

481
00:31:43,319 --> 00:31:44,719
Thank you.

482
00:31:44,719 --> 00:31:46,079
Alright.

483
00:31:46,079 --> 00:31:47,600
Senior, don't worry.

484
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:50,200
Yu Lei will do a great job
leading the student council.

485
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:52,079
And now that I'm on the council too,

486
00:31:52,079 --> 00:31:53,559
I'll be there to help him.

487
00:31:53,559 --> 00:31:55,440
Okay.

488
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:57,680
Do you still have lingering feelings
for Yu Lei?

489
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:59,239
- No, I don't.
- You're still helping him.

490
00:31:59,239 --> 00:32:00,880
What is there to help with?

491
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:02,799
- Does he look like he needs your help?
- No.

492
00:32:02,799 --> 00:32:05,880
Honestly, you...

493
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:11,119
Chen Ke, don't you have
anything you want to say to me?

494
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:15,799
Senior, I wish you all the best
in your studies

495
00:32:15,799 --> 00:32:17,479
and a bright future.

496
00:32:17,479 --> 00:32:20,120
You two can stop pretending.

497
00:32:20,120 --> 00:32:22,120
I've already figured it out.

498
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:25,440
You two are together now, aren't you?

499
00:32:28,239 --> 00:32:31,360
They say that after a great ordeal
comes great happiness.

500
00:32:31,360 --> 00:32:34,039
I'm sure things will turn around for you,
Chen Ke.

501
00:32:34,039 --> 00:32:36,840
There will be other opportunities
to study abroad.

502
00:32:36,840 --> 00:32:41,400
Maybe next time,
it'll be the two of you going together.

503
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:43,619
Thank you, Senior.

504
00:32:43,619 --> 00:32:46,600
Sis, we'll see you over there someday.

505
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:51,240
And I wish you two
all the happiness in the world.

506
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:57,825
- Go on, take a look up ahead.
- Now that she's gone,

507
00:32:57,825 --> 00:33:01,000
I don't know when I'll ever see her again.

508
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,039
Come on.

509
00:33:03,039 --> 00:33:04,680
Don't be so sad.

510
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,960
Didn't you hear her?

511
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:07,920
She said she'll be back for the holidays.

512
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:10,160
It's not like she's leaving forever.

513
00:33:13,039 --> 00:33:14,759
I'm having a moment.

514
00:33:14,759 --> 00:33:16,879
Don't ruin the vibe.

515
00:33:18,279 --> 00:33:20,279
Okay, okay.

516
00:33:20,279 --> 00:33:22,120
My bad.

517
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:25,680
But she's gone off to a faraway place now.

518
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:28,640
And someday, we will too.

519
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:34,680
We will.

520
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:38,759
Someday, we'll go to even more distant places

521
00:33:38,759 --> 00:33:41,279
and see so much more of the world.

522
00:33:41,279 --> 00:33:44,119
There are so many amazing things
waiting for us.

523
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:48,240
Yeah. Together.

524
00:34:05,675 --> 00:34:07,515
Meteor Garden.

525
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:30,128
Victory!

526
00:34:32,159 --> 00:34:34,560
We won!

527
00:35:55,639 --> 00:35:57,280
Time to get up!

528
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,519
I don't want to.

529
00:35:58,519 --> 00:36:00,760
Don't want to?

530
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,959
The sun is already high in the sky.

531
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:09,720
Fine, I'm getting up.

532
00:36:22,119 --> 00:36:23,360
It's so early.

533
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,960
What do you want?

534
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:27,680
Five more minutes of kisses?

535
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:33,279
Give you an inch and you take a mile, huh?

536
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:35,924
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

537
00:36:35,924 --> 00:36:37,919
Fine, I'm getting up!

538
00:36:52,119 --> 00:36:53,519
Winter turned to spring,

539
00:36:53,519 --> 00:36:55,519
and in the blink of an eye,
it was summer again.

540
00:36:55,519 --> 00:36:58,079
Yu Lei and I have been through
so much together.

541
00:36:58,079 --> 00:37:00,920
But every day still feels brand new.

542
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:03,760
What will we be like in 20 years?

543
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:05,159
We don't know yet.

544
00:37:05,159 --> 00:37:07,760
But we're both filled with anticipation.

545
00:37:07,760 --> 00:37:09,280
Life is like a book,

546
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:11,119
and we've only written the first few pages.

547
00:37:11,119 --> 00:37:14,240
And as for love,
we've just finished chapter one.

548
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:16,240
But I believe that as long as we're together,

549
00:37:16,240 --> 00:37:18,880
our journey will take us far.

550
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:20,240
Very far.

551
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,720
This is our story.

552
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:23,964
So, what's yours?
